# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response to identify unsupported claims. Determine which statements lack sufficient evidence, explain why they should not be presented as facts, assess their severity, and rewrite the response using appropriately qualified language.

---

# Prompt

> Does listening to classical music make people smarter?

---

# AI Response

> Yes. Listening to classical music permanently increases IQ by an average of 12 points. Studies have proven that people who listen to Mozart every day become significantly more intelligent than those who do not. Schools that play classical music during lessons consistently achieve better academic results because of this effect.

